{
 "name": "RPlog_Judgement_Passed",
 "title": "Judgement Passed",
 "summary": "Aboard the Star Destroyer Inquisitor's interrogation wing, Captain Jal'Dana Rall arrives to pass judgment on Flight Officer Damien 'Loki' Katon, a disgraced TIE pilot condemned for treason during wartime. Director Korynn Fleming reports on the prisoner's tortured confession while Commander Krieg and a pair of stormtroopers attend. Rall confronts the unrepentant Katon, who defends his actions as service to the true Empire and refuses to kneel to Emperor Vadim; Fleming reads the lengthy charges and Krieg offers grim parting words. When Katon declares he chooses death before dishonor, Rall executes him with a single blaster bolt to the head, orders his remains disposed of like garbage, and leaves with Krieg to discuss further matters.",
